lead_paragraph: English golfers Chris Wood and Matt Fitzpatrick secured easy first-round wins at the Paul Lawrie Match Play on Thursday as they look for a victory to cement a place in Europe's Ryder Cup team for the first time.

headline.print_headline: Wood, Fitzpatrick Advance at Paul Lawrie Match Play
